    "note": "Design-first artifact only \u2014 describes the MCP tool surface, not a running server. Tool input/output schemas $ref the same object schemas as the OpenAPI; each tool maps to an OpenAPI operationId. Surfaces SCA's open capital-plan and procurement data (capital projects, upcoming contracts, RFP solicitations, prequalified vendors, enrollment/capacity, inspections) and adds apply_for_prequalification \u2014 the net-new vendor write workflow locked today inside the bidset SharePoint portal.",
